parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Clarion/Bose in-dash CD player can cause the CD player to become inoperable, displaying an "ERR2" code, and making a clicking sound. This can lead to frustration and inconvenience for the driver.
symptoms: The CD player displays an "ERR2" code
the CD player makes a clicking sound
the CD player is unable to play or eject CDs
the CD player is stuck and cannot be retrieved.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the frame can lead to structural failure, causing the vehicle to collapse or lose control, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Rust and corrosion on the frame

and on the underbody; collapse of the frame while being lifted; inability to repair due to structural unsafety; rusted brackets and support beams on running boards; rusted strut tower housing; rust spreading along the undercarriage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the running boards can cause injuries to passengers entering or exiting the vehicle, particularly the elderly, disabled, or children.
symptoms: Rusted brackets and support beams on running boards; collapse of running boards when stepped on; inability to repair or replace due to high cost or design flaws.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Corrosion of Frame and Suspension Components
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the frame and suspension components can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Abnormal noises from the rear or front of the vehicle
grinding noise from the front wheel
vehicle pulls hard to one side
steering wheel is hard to turn
rear suspension bottoms out with multiple passengers.
